header.gameNote: BIG WEST CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

article.description: Khalil Ahmad had 28 points as Cal State Fullerton topped UC Santa Barbara 64-58 in the Big West Conference Tourney semifinals on Friday night.
article.headline: Ahmad leads Cal St.-Fullerton over UC Santa Barbara 64-58
article.linkText: Ahmad leads Cal St.-Fullerton over UC Santa Barbara 64-58
article.story: ANAHEIM, Calif. -- Khalil Ahmad had 28 points as Cal State Fullerton topped UC Santa Barbara 64-58 in the Big West Conference Tourney semifinals on Friday night. Kyle Allman Jr. had 12 points for Cal State Fullerton (16-16). Amadou Sow had 14 points for the Gauchos (22-10). Max Heidegger added 14 points and six rebounds. Ar'mond Davis had seven rebounds. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap , using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
